1
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:41,120
{\an8}Why is Punlop targeting you?

2
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:42,920
{\an8}Can you just leave me alone? Let go!

3
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:50,600
{\an8}Tell me the truth. How is 3C Corp.
planning to release the pathogen?

4
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,360
{\an8}<i>Punlop…</i>

5
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:55,040
{\an8}killed your father.

6
00:02:57,800 --> 00:03:00,840
{\an8}Remember this.
If Rin ever finds out, you're dead!

7
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,840
We need to talk.

8
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,320
I have nothing to say to you.

9
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,320
Then we don't have to talk.

10
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,400
I'm not letting you go anywhere.

11
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,960
If you want to throw a tantrum,
why not do it in your own room?

12
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,640
This isn't your room either!

13
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:45,000
I wish Taiga could see you
acting like a mad dog right now.

14
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:49,200
You think I'm the only mad dog here?

15
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:53,280
Do you know who Taiga is with right now?

16
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:57,960
Do you know who's in his house,

17
00:04:58,040 --> 00:05:01,720
in his room, in his bed? Who?

18
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:05,520
- Rin.
- Speechless, huh?

19
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:08,400
You love asking men for help, don't you?

20
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,760
"I want this, I want that."

21
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:13,520
Someone who didn't even ask

22
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:15,440
got straight into the house.

23
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,440
Rin.

24
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:20,040
Taiga is with Rin.

25
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,920
Rin, are you okay?

26
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:52,320
Okay, Aru. We're talking here.

27
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,240
Techut admitted

28
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,480
that Fire Phoenix created the pathogen

29
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:18,000
because they want to sell
the medicine and the vaccine.

30
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,680
Rin.

31
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:23,960
You're not a bad person.
Help me stop this.

32
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,040
I can't help you right now.

33
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,920
Punlop is targeting you.

34
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,720
Everyone you care about

35
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:34,400
is in danger right now, both Aru and Sun.

36
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,520
I know you're sick.

37
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,520
You need me to protect you.

38
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:58,480
What? I said it's canceled. Hello?

39
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,560
Hello?

40
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:37,800
PUNLOP

41
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:44,640
There's no negotiation, Taiga.

42
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,480
Have Rin give me her father's hard drive

43
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,120
in exchange for Ratee's life.

44
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:57,080
That's mine!

45
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:07,360
What's on this?

46
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:11,080
Punlop wants this hard drive.

47
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:13,760
Otherwise, Ratee dies!

48
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:58,280
I underestimated a pretty girl like you.
When I reviewed all the cameras,

49
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,800
I saw that you helped Dhammatat.

50
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:06,200
You bought up 3C Corp. shares.

51
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:11,080
You knew it was a nominee, rigged stocks,
and laundered money for Fire Phoenix.

52
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:16,400
The 3C pathogen would make
your father insanely rich

53
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:19,160
and put the entire economy
under your control.

54
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,640
Does Taiga know

55
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:29,800
what you're thinking
and what you're going to do?

56
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,760
With that face,

57
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:40,240
- it means…
- How many million?

58
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,360
Huh?

59
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,880
How many millions do you want?

60
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:46,320
To spare Taiga's life?

61
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:48,920
Yes, I'll pay you right now.

62
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:55,720
How many million?

63
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,560
Would a hundred million be enough?

64
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,920
If you overestimate yourself,

65
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:08,920
you'll end up just a servant,
working for someone else until you die.

66
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,480
Not someone who gives orders,

67
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:16,200
not someone who wields money as power.

68
00:10:17,760 --> 00:10:19,600
And if you kill Taiga,

69
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:23,280
I'll use everything my father has,

70
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:27,080
money, influence,

71
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:30,200
to destroy your life,
until you wish you were dead.

72
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:51,080
Punlop's trying to kill you

73
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:54,800
because this hard drive
holds Fire Phoenix's secrets.

74
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,960
Stay here until I get back.

75
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,560
Wait.

76
00:11:19,640 --> 00:11:21,160
Take it and help your girl.

77
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:24,640
Save Ratee's life.

78
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:28,680
I know you're not a weak woman.

79
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:32,760
You've always been stronger
than anyone else.

80
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:39,400
You don't have to force yourself.

81
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,720
I'll make Ratee understand…

82
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:46,800
that I love a woman who tried to kill me.

83
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:53,480
I love her without ever thinking
about the end.

84
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:59,280
Everything has an end.

85
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:02,640
For me,

86
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:06,320
happiness doesn't last forever.

87
00:12:26,040 --> 00:12:29,240
Help Ratee, the one who loves you.

88
00:13:37,680 --> 00:13:38,800
Taiga.

89
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,480
What about my niece?

90
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:48,480
This is all you want, isn't it?

91
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,000
Rin handed it over so easily.

92
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:56,040
Love really does make people stupid.

93
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:58,800
Let Ratee go.

94
00:14:25,280 --> 00:14:26,360
Ratee!

95
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:40,800
Taiga!

96
00:14:55,280 --> 00:14:57,320
Don't worry about me.
Go catch him, quickly!

97
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,560
Get over here.

98
00:16:13,800 --> 00:16:16,040
Let go! I have to get Punlop.

99
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:17,400
But he will kill you.

100
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:20,960
I know you're worried,
but I have to handle this myself.

101
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:35,040
Don't go, Rin! Let Khanin go after him.

102
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:41,840
Rin!

103
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:43,800
Shit.

104
00:17:13,119 --> 00:17:14,480
Mr. Naruban.

105
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:16,839
Rin sent us to help.

106
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:19,800
All cameras are off.
We've got three minutes.

107
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,839
The guards and workers have been sedated.

108
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:23,680
Then hurry.

109
00:17:24,319 --> 00:17:25,599
We'll get you somewhere safe.

110
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:35,200
What are you doing to Mr. Naruban?

111
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:47,960
Let's go.

112
00:18:28,360 --> 00:18:29,280
Are you okay, my dear?

113
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:31,160
Ugh.

114
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:36,040
Dad!

115
00:18:45,360 --> 00:18:46,400
Dad.

116
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:49,800
Uncle Punlop must pay for shooting you.

117
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:52,800
I'm going to do the work
you gave your life for.

118
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:56,440
I'll go after Damon myself.

119
00:18:57,800 --> 00:19:00,120
I'll take down Fire Phoenix for you.

120
00:19:05,360 --> 00:19:07,960
You can't even watch over one person.

121
00:19:18,040 --> 00:19:21,200
Send a letter to the shareholders
and the board,

122
00:19:21,280 --> 00:19:24,520
saying Mr. Naruban is in a coma
and I'll take over.

123
00:19:24,600 --> 00:19:26,360
Anyone who disagrees, report to me.

124
00:19:26,960 --> 00:19:29,040
Aren't we having a board meeting?

125
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:32,880
Alright, no meeting.

126
00:19:32,960 --> 00:19:35,600
I'll quickly email everyone.

127
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:38,520
Within one hour. Anyone with an issue,

128
00:19:38,600 --> 00:19:40,320
give me their names.

129
00:19:41,760 --> 00:19:42,600
Yes.

130
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:53,160
This is all the evidence Phumin collected…

131
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:55,480
…on Fire Phoenix.

132
00:19:55,560 --> 00:19:56,640
NARUBAN - CEO 3C
GIRANUN, TECHUT, NUNNAPAT

133
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:57,680
PRIN - DEAD, SABAIPRAE - DEAD

134
00:19:57,760 --> 00:19:58,800
POK - UNFOUND, PRAB - UNFOUND
PUN - UNFOUND

135
00:19:58,880 --> 00:20:01,480
Punlop's probably scared of being exposed.

136
00:20:02,440 --> 00:20:03,840
But at this rate,

137
00:20:04,840 --> 00:20:06,120
he won't stay quiet,

138
00:20:07,360 --> 00:20:08,480
neither Punlop nor Damon.

139
00:20:08,560 --> 00:20:10,360
Force them out of hiding.

140
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:15,880
And we'll unmask them.

141
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:21,080
NARUMIT - BROTHER, CAR CRASH, DISABLED

142
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:22,720
Rin's hunting Punlop just like us.

143
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:28,920
Will Rin help you?

144
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:30,360
Even if she doesn't,

145
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:33,600
I'm sure she won't get in our way again.

146
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,800
Please, Khanin.

147
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:37,680
Don't hurt Rin.

148
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:39,880
Fine.

149
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:41,840
But remember, Taiga.

150
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:45,160
Your past and your family,

151
00:20:46,480 --> 00:20:48,520
Phumin protected them with his life.

152
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:52,080
Don't let good people die

153
00:20:52,160 --> 00:20:53,640
in vain.

154
00:21:17,520 --> 00:21:20,280
Board member Surachet was in a car crash
this morning and is in a coma.

155
00:21:20,360 --> 00:21:22,360
As for Lady Ploy,

156
00:21:22,440 --> 00:21:24,120
a major shareholder,

157
00:21:24,840 --> 00:21:26,200
her mansion caught fire.

158
00:21:26,280 --> 00:21:28,560
She was trapped inside and inhaled smoke.

159
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:32,240
She's not doing well.
Her heart stopped once already.

160
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:37,960
Both of them

161
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:41,080
are against you
taking over for Mr. Naruban.

162
00:21:41,160 --> 00:21:45,680
They've emailed the other board members,
saying they'll oppose you to the fullest.

163
00:21:47,520 --> 00:21:51,000
You think I'd kill anyone
who disagrees with me?

164
00:21:54,720 --> 00:21:56,880
I've worked for a long time.

165
00:21:56,960 --> 00:22:00,360
I'm ready to serve you, Mrs. Giranun,

166
00:22:00,440 --> 00:22:03,200
just like I devoted myself to Mr. Naruban.

167
00:22:04,120 --> 00:22:05,200
Very good.

168
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:07,960
From now on, you're mine.

169
00:22:08,040 --> 00:22:11,880
Report everything from 3C Corp. to me,
when I'm not at work.

170
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:15,600
Yes.

171
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,560
Thank you so much

172
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:35,120
for handling
those two ridiculous board members.

173
00:22:39,080 --> 00:22:41,840
But Taiga still hasn't shown up
at 3C Corp.

174
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:44,200
I'll have Nun check again.

175
00:22:44,840 --> 00:22:46,680
I need to find Rin too.

176
00:22:48,280 --> 00:22:50,000
While you're tracking them down,

177
00:22:51,560 --> 00:22:54,120
I want you to move in here.

178
00:22:55,160 --> 00:22:58,280
Bring your people so they can help guard.

179
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:02,400
Okay.

180
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:05,920
I'll overhaul the entire
security system as well.

181
00:23:08,080 --> 00:23:09,640
Once we find Taiga

182
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:12,800
and Rin, we'll find Naruban too,

183
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:14,480
since they're working together.

184
00:23:15,520 --> 00:23:16,760
When that happens,

185
00:23:17,360 --> 00:23:19,360
take care of all of them.

186
00:23:20,480 --> 00:23:23,000
Anyone who helps, eliminate them.

187
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:26,080
I'm sick of them.

188
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:27,280
Okay.

189
00:23:32,800 --> 00:23:34,520
You already know who you are, don't you?

190
00:23:34,600 --> 00:23:35,960
That's why you came here.

191
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:41,360
Inspector Phumin's files

192
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:43,160
say the gunman who killed my family

193
00:23:43,840 --> 00:23:46,800
was one of your older brother
Narumit's workers.

194
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:51,880
All the gunmen have been dealt with.

195
00:23:53,480 --> 00:23:55,920
My brother didn't know anything
about the gunman.

196
00:23:58,920 --> 00:24:00,520
On the day Prin died,

197
00:24:02,040 --> 00:24:03,880
he saved one boy.

198
00:24:05,560 --> 00:24:06,920
My younger brother?

199
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:08,960
I'm not sure.

200
00:24:09,560 --> 00:24:11,080
But Narumit said

201
00:24:11,160 --> 00:24:13,320
the boy was left in front of the farm.

202
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,800
He was in shock,
couldn't remember anything.

203
00:24:16,320 --> 00:24:18,960
Feeling sorry for him,
he raised him until he grew up.

204
00:24:20,120 --> 00:24:21,240
Indhorn?

205
00:24:24,120 --> 00:24:27,240
I had a gut feeling
ever since Narumit's car accident.

206
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:31,240
It was around the same time news came out
that Fire Phoenix

207
00:24:31,760 --> 00:24:34,120
found the three children of Prin.

208
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:41,680
Then the leader of the Yakuza gang,

209
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:46,880
the Blazing Tiger, was killed.

210
00:24:47,640 --> 00:24:49,520
Dad Kenji died because of me.

211
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:54,240
Now Fire Phoenix is hunting
the three of us siblings.

212
00:24:54,320 --> 00:24:56,000
Calm down, Taiga.

213
00:24:56,080 --> 00:24:59,640
I believe your two younger brothers
are still safe.

214
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:04,080
But the moment
you give Fire Phoenix confidence

215
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:06,600
and confirm your brothers' identities,

216
00:25:07,520 --> 00:25:09,640
they'll be in immediate danger.

217
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:17,960
Here's the medicine.

218
00:25:19,040 --> 00:25:20,520
Here you go.

219
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:28,440
I tried giving these to the workers.
They got better.

220
00:25:30,800 --> 00:25:34,760
This medicine really works.
It can cure the disease, right?

221
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:36,640
Yes.

222
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:41,680
My workers who were sick with Ms. Rin
took it continuously for months.

223
00:25:41,760 --> 00:25:44,960
Their bodies got better,
breathing easier, and less tired.

224
00:25:45,560 --> 00:25:46,800
Exactly!

225
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:50,160
Rin gets tired easily
and once mentioned bleeding.

226
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:52,640
It's probably because
of the anti-pathogen medicine.

227
00:25:52,720 --> 00:25:55,320
Then should we try giving Ms. Rin
the medicine?

228
00:25:55,840 --> 00:25:58,440
It's natural, no chemicals.

229
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:02,240
It can fight the pathogens and vaccines.

230
00:26:02,320 --> 00:26:03,440
I'll bring it over.

231
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:12,720
<i>On the day Prin died,</i>

232
00:26:12,800 --> 00:26:14,920
<i>he saved one boy.</i>

233
00:26:20,720 --> 00:26:22,520
I just came from Mr. Naruban's farm,

234
00:26:23,640 --> 00:26:24,920
so I stopped by here.

235
00:26:27,880 --> 00:26:30,920
I'll head back to the farm.
I've got some business.

236
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:32,200
Okay.

237
00:26:49,080 --> 00:26:50,480
I need to see Rin, Aru.

238
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:55,200
Rin usually contacts us herself,
like when we helped Mr. Naruban.

239
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:58,600
Mr. Indhorn also wants
to give Rin the medicine,

240
00:26:58,680 --> 00:27:00,360
but I don't know how to reach her.

241
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:03,880
Right now,

242
00:27:04,520 --> 00:27:06,160
how sick is Rin?

243
00:27:09,520 --> 00:27:12,120
I know you're worried about Rin.

244
00:27:13,280 --> 00:27:16,000
We love Rin, and we're worried too.

245
00:27:16,600 --> 00:27:20,480
But whatever we can do now,
we have to do it fast.

246
00:27:26,240 --> 00:27:29,840
My son and I don't know
where the pathogen was stored.

247
00:27:30,520 --> 00:27:31,920
I really don't know.

248
00:27:32,520 --> 00:27:34,720
Is there any way
to force Fire Phoenix to act?

249
00:27:34,800 --> 00:27:37,200
If 3C Corp. is a nominee
laundering money for Fire Phoenix,

250
00:27:37,720 --> 00:27:39,600
we should strike there.

251
00:27:39,680 --> 00:27:41,840
Don't let my employees
get caught up in this.

252
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:45,400
They're not part of anyone's grudge.

253
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:48,200
Then who is Damon?

254
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:52,200
Not me.

255
00:27:53,440 --> 00:27:55,160
And no one knows.

256
00:27:55,680 --> 00:27:57,680
Damon's identity has never been revealed.

257
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:01,440
We have to lure Damon out,

258
00:28:01,520 --> 00:28:03,320
tear off that mask.

259
00:28:04,960 --> 00:28:07,760
No one else should suffer
because of their greed.

260
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:13,480
Nun, I need to talk.

261
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:17,080
The purchase volume, the investment
in 3C-Coin, it's plummeting,

262
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:19,440
even though 3C-Coin
is backed by its reputation.

263
00:28:19,520 --> 00:28:20,920
Why is this happening?

264
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:22,640
It used to be fine.

265
00:28:22,720 --> 00:28:25,920
But after news of Dad's illness
and you taking over management,

266
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:26,960
people lost confidence.

267
00:28:27,040 --> 00:28:30,000
Then restore their confidence.
You can do that, right?

268
00:28:31,120 --> 00:28:33,360
Credibility isn't built in a day.

269
00:28:34,280 --> 00:28:35,920
We should hold off on the coin for now.

270
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:38,520
No. We won't stop anything.

271
00:28:38,600 --> 00:28:41,440
We must get as many people as possible
to invest in our coin.

272
00:28:41,520 --> 00:28:44,120
We'll change the world with our coin.

273
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:45,520
Our coin will have value,

274
00:28:45,600 --> 00:28:48,440
backed by gold, and tied to the US Dollar.

275
00:28:49,120 --> 00:28:51,760
We'll collect as much cash
as possible from coin sales.

276
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:54,800
I've already set a target, a billion.

277
00:28:55,560 --> 00:28:57,280
What about the returns?

278
00:28:57,360 --> 00:29:00,440
If the coin can't actually be used,
isn't that just tricking people

279
00:29:00,520 --> 00:29:02,960
into investing
and giving us money for free?

280
00:29:03,040 --> 00:29:04,400
People holding our coin

281
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:07,960
will get the right to buy shares
in the pharma and vaccine factories.

282
00:29:08,040 --> 00:29:11,240
We'll make the best medicine and vaccines
to protect ourselves.

283
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:14,800
Medicine? Medicine or pathogens?

284
00:29:20,760 --> 00:29:23,400
So it's you, the one helping your dad,
helping Techut.

285
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:26,080
Mom, stop!

286
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:27,600
You're doing something wrong.

287
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:32,440
Let go!

288
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:34,160
Let go!

289
00:29:34,760 --> 00:29:36,600
Weren't you going to do as I ordered?

290
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:39,920
I can do anything,
but I won't kill my own family.

291
00:29:44,520 --> 00:29:45,920
You have to choose.

292
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:49,720
You want to win,
to prove yourself, don't you?

293
00:29:49,800 --> 00:29:53,080
Yes, but not with him getting in the way!

294
00:29:53,160 --> 00:29:54,640
How is he any better than Dad

295
00:29:54,720 --> 00:29:56,680
that you'd be foolish enough
to let him use you?

296
00:29:59,120 --> 00:30:00,440
I'll take care of your daughter.

297
00:30:02,720 --> 00:30:04,160
Calm down, okay?

298
00:30:08,960 --> 00:30:10,440
Mom!

299
00:30:11,080 --> 00:30:12,040
Mom!

300
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:15,360
Let me go! Let go!

301
00:30:15,440 --> 00:30:16,600
I said let me go!

302
00:30:22,800 --> 00:30:24,160
How's Mr. Naruban?

303
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:26,360
He's okay.

304
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:30,520
But are you okay? Where are you now?

305
00:30:33,280 --> 00:30:35,760
The less you know,
the safer you'll be, Aru.

306
00:30:36,280 --> 00:30:38,000
Take care of yourself.

307
00:30:38,080 --> 00:30:40,400
Tell Sun and Dhammatat too.

308
00:30:41,080 --> 00:30:42,960
Hey, Mr. Taiga came to the farm.

309
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:46,560
He checked on Mr. Naruban,

310
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:48,640
then went to Mr. Indhorn's farm.

311
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:57,360
Don't let Taiga know you can contact me.

312
00:30:57,960 --> 00:30:59,720
Don't stay alone anymore.

313
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:01,800
<i>Lee.</i>

314
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:04,560
Whatever you do next, let me know.

315
00:31:06,880 --> 00:31:09,360
That's it for now, Aru.
Take care of yourself.

316
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:12,400
Lee, don't hang up yet! Lee!

317
00:31:40,760 --> 00:31:41,800
Aru.

318
00:31:44,240 --> 00:31:45,400
Where's Lee?

319
00:31:48,080 --> 00:31:49,760
Can you not ask, Sun?

320
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:53,760
I can't.

321
00:31:54,720 --> 00:31:56,240
I can't say anything.

322
00:31:56,760 --> 00:31:58,800
But Lee is our friend, Aru.

323
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:06,920
Do everything you can, Sun.

324
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:09,960
Finish 3C Corp. and Fire Phoenix
once and for all.

325
00:32:11,120 --> 00:32:14,280
Then our friend Lee
can return to her normal life.

326
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:38,160
Any progress from the two farms?

327
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:40,400
Mr. Naruban and Techut are safe.

328
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:45,280
What about Rin?
What are you going to do, Taiga?

329
00:32:47,520 --> 00:32:49,160
Find her as fast as possible.

330
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:52,720
If you don't find her,
you'll keep looking?

331
00:32:57,760 --> 00:32:59,720
I'm confident Rin can help us.

332
00:33:03,760 --> 00:33:06,040
If there's anything I can help with,
just tell me.

333
00:33:06,120 --> 00:33:07,800
3C Corp. is my responsibility.

334
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:20,320
Taiga, I'll continue the investigation.

335
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:23,040
Fire Phoenix has several safe houses.

336
00:33:23,120 --> 00:33:25,320
If we're going in,
we need to block all escape routes.

337
00:33:26,040 --> 00:33:27,040
If we're lucky,

338
00:33:27,120 --> 00:33:29,160
we might find Rin lurking nearby.

339
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:49,000
The one who reopened your family's case

340
00:33:49,080 --> 00:33:50,640
was Inspector Phumin.

341
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:53,600
He has a daughter.

342
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:57,600
She's the one who inherited
everything from her father.

343
00:33:58,200 --> 00:33:59,320
Hard drive

344
00:34:00,280 --> 00:34:02,000
from Inspector Phumin.

345
00:34:02,600 --> 00:34:04,400
She just found out that her father

346
00:34:04,920 --> 00:34:06,600
was shot by Fire Phoenix.

347
00:34:07,280 --> 00:34:08,960
Are you telling me

348
00:34:09,760 --> 00:34:13,080
that Rin is Inspector Phumin's daughter?

349
00:34:13,600 --> 00:34:15,040
Yes.

350
00:34:16,080 --> 00:34:17,679
I just confirmed it.

351
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:23,320
Rin had a plan all along.

352
00:34:23,920 --> 00:34:26,000
She wasn't fooled by Fire Phoenix.

353
00:34:26,080 --> 00:34:28,199
She went along with them

354
00:34:28,719 --> 00:34:31,760
to use Punlop to get to Damon.

355
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:37,199
But she only just realized it was Punlop
who killed her father.

356
00:34:38,440 --> 00:34:40,719
I'm the one at fault
for only telling her now.

357
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:05,120
Help Rin, Taiga.

358
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:10,040
Don't let anything happen to her
like her father.

359
00:35:11,520 --> 00:35:12,720
Rin.

360
00:35:14,240 --> 00:35:16,240
You can't take out Punlop on your own.

361
00:35:19,360 --> 00:35:20,680
Come back to me.

362
00:35:22,680 --> 00:35:25,040
We'll take down our revenge together.

363
00:35:57,480 --> 00:35:58,640
<i>Dad.</i>

364
00:36:00,640 --> 00:36:02,360
<i>We'll see each other soon.</i>

365
00:36:03,320 --> 00:36:05,480
<i>I will finally be with you.</i>

366
00:36:30,240 --> 00:36:31,920
3C-Coin is crashing again.

367
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:35,600
Who's trying to bring it down?

368
00:36:45,560 --> 00:36:47,280
Damon called an urgent meeting.

369
00:38:12,200 --> 00:38:15,000
Welcome, members of Fire Phoenix.

370
00:38:15,600 --> 00:38:17,920
This is the most important meeting,

371
00:38:18,520 --> 00:38:22,760
the one where Fire Phoenix
will change the world.

372
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:25,200
Fire Phoenix

373
00:38:25,840 --> 00:38:29,040
will have its own nation,
built on our coin.

374
00:38:32,160 --> 00:38:34,880
From now on, every command in the world

375
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:36,880
will depend on Fire Phoenix.

376
00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:41,920
I will change the world with our coin.

377
00:38:43,080 --> 00:38:45,640
Every country will have to use
the same currency.

378
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:49,400
Our coin will have value in the system,

379
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:51,280
usable in online casinos

380
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:53,840
or to buy the newest,

381
00:38:53,920 --> 00:38:55,360
most advanced weapons.

382
00:38:56,160 --> 00:38:59,280
Our coin will be asset-backed by gold

383
00:38:59,360 --> 00:39:01,880
and equal in value to the US Dollar.

384
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:09,800
<i>We won't stop anything.</i>

385
00:39:09,880 --> 00:39:13,000
We must get as many people as possible
to invest in our coin.

386
00:39:13,080 --> 00:39:15,280
We'll change the world with our coin.

387
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:16,680
Our coin will have value,

388
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:19,400
backed by gold, and tied to the US Dollar.

389
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:22,120
We'll collect as much cash as possible
from coin sales.

390
00:39:22,200 --> 00:39:25,360
I've already set a target, a billion.

391
00:39:30,320 --> 00:39:31,720
The pathogen war

392
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:35,320
will make our coin
as valuable as human life.

393
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:39,080
Fire Phoenix will lock down
the entire world,

394
00:39:39,160 --> 00:39:41,800
controlling every country
with biological weapons.

395
00:39:41,880 --> 00:39:44,440
Equality and justice

396
00:39:44,520 --> 00:39:46,080
must prevail.

397
00:39:47,240 --> 00:39:50,080
Equality! Justice!

398
00:39:50,160 --> 00:39:53,320
Equality! Justice!

399
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:56,720
Equality! Justice!

400
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:59,640
Equality! Justice!

401
00:39:59,720 --> 00:40:01,320
Equality!

402
00:40:32,120 --> 00:40:33,240
Hey.

403
00:40:58,280 --> 00:41:00,560
Ratee, help me!

404
00:41:00,640 --> 00:41:02,600
I've been captured in the house.

405
00:41:02,680 --> 00:41:04,040
Come save me!

406
00:43:35,200 --> 00:43:36,280
Taiga!

407
00:43:36,360 --> 00:43:37,840
Calm down, Taiga!

408
00:43:41,240 --> 00:43:42,880
Damon won't come out again.

409
00:43:43,600 --> 00:43:45,680
We've already lost our best chance.

410
00:43:45,760 --> 00:43:47,560
But we still have 3C Corp.

411
00:43:49,520 --> 00:43:51,680
Yes. I can still get in there.

412
00:43:52,320 --> 00:43:55,120
Even if Giranun blocks me, I have ways.

413
00:43:56,240 --> 00:43:57,600
There are many who don't agree

414
00:43:57,680 --> 00:44:00,320
with Giranun taking over for Mr. Naruban.

415
00:44:00,400 --> 00:44:03,360
I'll bring them over, pressure 3C Corp.

416
00:44:03,440 --> 00:44:05,280
to stop being a money-laundering front
for Fire Phoenix.

417
00:44:05,800 --> 00:44:06,680
Push them from every angle.

418
00:44:09,600 --> 00:44:12,440
But the key question is,
where is the pathogen now?

419
00:44:13,440 --> 00:44:15,600
It's Damon's final card.

420
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:17,600
If he releases it, it's over.

421
00:44:20,040 --> 00:44:21,800
Naruban and Techut don't know.

422
00:44:26,760 --> 00:44:28,000
But Ms. Nun might.

423
00:44:29,600 --> 00:44:31,920
She could find a lead for us.

424
00:44:32,000 --> 00:44:34,120
Ms. Nun is safe now.

425
00:44:34,200 --> 00:44:35,960
Dhammatat sent a message.

426
00:44:36,040 --> 00:44:38,480
She's on her way to Mr. Naruban's farm.

427
00:44:38,560 --> 00:44:39,560
Good.

428
00:44:44,040 --> 00:44:46,520
We need to take away
all of Damon's leverage.

429
00:45:03,640 --> 00:45:06,160
You said you'd upgraded
the security system.

430
00:45:06,240 --> 00:45:08,000
How could Taiga get to Nun?

431
00:45:08,080 --> 00:45:10,760
If I wasn't in the building today
and if I'd been here?

432
00:45:13,880 --> 00:45:16,400
- You were at 3C Corp. today?
- Yes.

433
00:45:17,280 --> 00:45:18,400
Didn't go anywhere?

434
00:45:19,520 --> 00:45:22,320
Yes. Why?

435
00:45:25,000 --> 00:45:26,520
I'm wondering,

436
00:45:28,120 --> 00:45:30,400
where did the pathogen Techut created go?

437
00:45:31,560 --> 00:45:32,680
Who's keeping it?

438
00:45:36,960 --> 00:45:38,160
Do you have any idea

439
00:45:39,200 --> 00:45:42,080
where your son would store
something this important?

440
00:45:43,360 --> 00:45:44,680
I don't know.

441
00:45:46,320 --> 00:45:48,120
Based on what Ms. Nun said the other day,

442
00:45:50,680 --> 00:45:53,160
is it possible it's at 3C Corp.?

443
00:45:55,480 --> 00:45:58,240
If the pathogen is a weapon
that can destroy our enemies,

444
00:46:01,440 --> 00:46:03,640
why not put it to use for our benefit?

445
00:46:07,840 --> 00:46:10,880
- Unless you're worried about your husband.
- I want him dead!

446
00:46:17,560 --> 00:46:18,720
And for you,

447
00:46:19,560 --> 00:46:21,920
Naruban deserved to die
a long time ago, right?

448
00:46:34,000 --> 00:46:35,120
{\an8}You can't die.

449
00:46:35,200 --> 00:46:38,360
{\an8}Don't sacrifice yourself alone.
You still have me.

450
00:46:38,440 --> 00:46:40,360
{\an8}<i>Let me die alone, Taiga.</i>

451
00:46:40,440 --> 00:46:42,440
{\an8}Then you can be with the woman
who loves you.

452
00:46:42,520 --> 00:46:44,840
{\an8}Fire Phoenix is finding a way
to release the pathogen.

453
00:46:44,920 --> 00:46:46,720
{\an8}Release it at their own event?

454
00:46:47,320 --> 00:46:50,040
{\an8}<i>Goodbye, you foul-mouthed kid.</i>

455
00:46:50,120 --> 00:46:51,640
{\an8}<i>Hope you die happily.</i>

456
00:46:54,880 --> 00:46:55,840
{\an8}Whoa!

457
00:47:27,640 --> 00:47:29,440
Subtitle translation by:
Chomchanach Yanaharn

